Approval(address,address,uint256).details: Emitted when `owner` enables `approved` to manage the `tokenId` token.

ApprovalForAll(address,address,bool).details: Emitted when `owner` enables or disables (`approved`) `operator` to manage all of its assets.

Transfer(address,address,uint256).details: Emitted when `tokenId` token is transferred from `from` to `to`.

buyTicket().details: This function is used to buy tickets for a Drake concert

params._startTime: set the start time of the ticket sale

getEndTime().details: returns the end time of purchase

getMaxSoulNBoundCounter().details: returns the count of each soulbount received

getMaxTicketAmount().details: returns the maximum amount of ticket that can be purchased

getPreSaleCounter().details: returns the count of each presale acquired

getPresaleMaxAmount().details: returns the maximum presale ticket sale

getTicketPrice().details: returns the amount of ticket price

isWhiteListed(address).details: checks if an address is whitelisted or not

killContract().details: kills the contract purchase are done, and transfer the remaining balance to the contract owner

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params.addresses: Addresses to be removed from the whitelist

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params.addresses: Addresses to be whitelisted for Pre-sale
